    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i think i get the formula part now, but it still feels like there's some kind of hidden mechanism eating away at my progress. it's almost like there's something working against me behind the scenes to keep the debt high. is there anything else besides the standard interest calculation that could be causing this much drag on my principal reduction?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
